'''Etsbergisk''' is ne Limbuurichske [[Sproake]], ju fon sowät 50 Moanskene boald wäd in [[Etsberg]]. In Etsberg kwäd me ''Etsbèrgersj''. 

Etsbergisk is uurs as uur Limbuurichske Sproake. In uur Limbuurichske Sproake is 'ou' (as in ''goud'' un ''Bouk'') 'oo', in Etsbergisk is dät 'à': ''good'' un ''gàd'' (goud) ''book'' un ''bàk'' (Bouk).

